symptoms of cough and wheezing and of the rapid ventricular response was unknown, and the outcome of 
unspecified heart issues was not recovered.  It was noted that the primary physician was unaware of the last 
hospitalization; however he was aware of the patient's previous hospitalizations.
Additional information has been requested.